Instructions
In this game you will be in control of Amanda, a young woman who has started her journey through a life full of magic, whether it is beauty or harmful.
You will fight zombies with both of your attacks (Mouse buttons 0 & 1) and you will be able to change your camera view partially with TAB.
Once you are playing, you can go back to the main menu with ESC and read the instructions, play again or exit the game.
Have fun! I hope you enjoy it :D
